item.description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This is Post 2 in the &lt;a href=&#34;/tags/agentic-os/&#34;&gt;Agentic OS series&lt;/a&gt; — the economics of using different LLMs for different jobs.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-12week-math-doesnt-work-without-this&#34;&gt;The $12/Week Math Doesn&amp;rsquo;t Work Without This&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In &lt;a href=&#34;/posts/agentic-os-12-week-team/&#34;&gt;Post 1&lt;/a&gt;, I claimed a $12/week AI operations team. The numbers:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Agent&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Model&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Weekly Cost&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/thead&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Hermes&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Kimi K2.5&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;~$1.50&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Dispatch&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;DeepSeek V3.2&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;~$0.80&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Builder&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Claude Code&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;~$3.00&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Verifier&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;DeepSeek V3.2&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;~$0.80&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Pamela&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;GPT-4.1 nano&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;~$6.00&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Total: ~$12.10&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If every agent used GPT-4.5? &lt;strong&gt;~$120/week&lt;/strong&gt;. 10x more expensive. Same output quality.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This is Post 1 in the &lt;a href=&#34;/tags/agentic-os/&#34;&gt;Agentic OS series&lt;/a&gt; — documenting how we built a self-managing AI operations team that runs 24/7 for less than a coffee budget.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-50k-question&#34;&gt;The $50K Question&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I was quoted $50,000 for a six-month retainer with a mid-market AI consultancy. They&amp;rsquo;d build &amp;ldquo;autonomous agents&amp;rdquo; for my creative systems business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I spent $12/week instead.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Not $12/day. &lt;strong&gt;$12/week&lt;/strong&gt;. Less than a Netflix subscription. Less than two burritos in San Francisco.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Today marks the completion of our technical SEO foundation. The site now ships with:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;whats-live&#34;&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s Live&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical SEO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive sitemap with weekly refresh&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;JSON-LD structured data (Organization, WebSite, WebPage, BlogPosting, CreativeWork, BreadcrumbList)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Canonical URLs and alternate formats&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;robots.txt with crawl directives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Semantic HTML with proper heading hierarchy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Social Sharing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open Graph meta tags for Facebook, LinkedIn, Discord&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Twitter Cards (summary_large_image)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dynamic image generation with proper 1200x630 dimensions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Page-specific titles and descriptions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
